{"tid":882811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金庸大俠走左 一人一句祝福佢","createTime":"2018-10-30T11:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T16:57:35.000Z","uid":167451,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8a98dbc28193c1c494595ea6e20613220be0077b","tid":882811,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"細筆名金庸、武俠小說泰斗查良鏞逝世，享年94歲。金庸筆下創作多部膾炙人口的武俠小說，包括《射鵰英雄傳》、《神鵰俠侶》、《倚天屠龍記》、《天龍八部》、《笑傲江湖》、《鹿鼎記》等。<br />\n<br />\n除了文學界外，查良鏞亦涉足傳媒界多年，1947年大學畢業後先受聘於上海《大公報》，任國際新聞編輯。1948年《大公報》香港版復刊，急需翻譯人員，查良鏞被報館調派來港，其後調任《新晚報》副刊編輯。<br />\n<br />\n1959年創辦《明報》；1968年又創辦主打娛樂、名人及時裝的《明報周刊》。1969年《明報晚報》創刊。《明報》在80年代急速發展，至1989年，當年65歲的查良鏞宣佈辭去社長一職。1993年查宣佈辭任董事局主席，向他一手創辦的《明報》正式告別。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58854863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58854863&d=bIkwlEUtBEDcqzqftKfRxMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f33a27dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58854863&h=77feee7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58854863</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個就睇你小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路好走<br />\n<br />\n金庸大俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97082ebd08824f6ef37f117fe5cc561ec5adb1e","tid":882811,"uid":294,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"「孩兒，你長大了之後，要提防女人騙你，越是好看的女人，越會騙人。」"},{"pid":"911f4bf8482cdb9d88d47c4426b545c754c10891","tid":882811,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"8a98dbc28193c1c494595ea6e20613220be0077b","tid":882811,"uid":167451,"like":0,"d